      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why im typing this. i just feel so incredibly tired. like, not just sleep tired, but every single part of my soul is just... done. the lab results came back and everything is basically ruined. the funding is gone. i spent 5 years on this and it's just zero. everything i am is tied to this work and now there's nothing left. i just want everything to stop. i just want the noise and the pressure to finally be quiet.",
